1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,020
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,020 --> 00:00:10,140
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,140 --> 00:00:15,300
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,300 --> 00:00:22,700
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:30,660
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:35,540
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:49,580
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,900 --> 00:00:54,220
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:54,940 --> 00:00:59,340
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:03,340
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:05,940
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,420 --> 00:01:10,060
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,420 --> 00:01:14,660
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:20,020
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:23,820
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,820 --> 00:01:26,420
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 37 =

20
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:39,980
What do you think?

21
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:43,020
= Dong Qiuhe =
The most exquisite tassel I’ve ever seen.

22
00:01:45,460 --> 00:01:47,380
Yesterday, when my brother and his wife came,

23
00:01:48,140 --> 00:01:50,060
Huan, my closest maid before,

24
00:01:50,060 --> 00:01:51,220
came with them.

25
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:52,940
She made it for me.

26
00:01:59,460 --> 00:02:00,340
She left the palace

27
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:02,460
due to a few mistakes, and got married.

28
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:10,260
Her husband was born poor.

29
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:12,380
He used to be a clerk

30
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:13,540
under my brother-in-law.

31
00:02:15,060 --> 00:02:15,820
Then Huan bought a small store

32
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:17,260
with the dowry

33
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:18,700
my mother gave her

34
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:21,860
to sell embroidery and clothes
to pay for his studies.

35
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:24,780
After eight years,

36
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:26,900
the once small store

37
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:27,860
has become famous

38
00:02:27,860 --> 00:02:29,340
in the Capital.

39
00:02:29,980 --> 00:02:32,420
Her husband studied hard and passed the exam.

40
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:35,420
Last year, he was appointed as
Assistant Magistrate of Hangzhou.

41
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:37,380
Now, he wants Huan and their three sons

42
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:38,540
and a daughter to go there, too.

43
00:02:39,740 --> 00:02:41,260
She came yesterday to bid me farewell,

44
00:02:44,660 --> 00:02:47,660
saying she would miss the Capital,

45
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:51,020
her store

46
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:55,500
and the Cao family.

47
00:02:56,660 --> 00:02:57,540
Your Highness,

48
00:02:57,540 --> 00:02:58,540
= Huan =

49
00:02:58,540 --> 00:03:00,220
allow me to call you Miss one last time.

50
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:02,220
I’ve finally realized

51
00:03:02,820 --> 00:03:04,180
how thoughtful you were

52
00:03:04,180 --> 00:03:05,260
when making me leave.

53
00:03:06,180 --> 00:03:08,460
Since I was young, I always assumed

54
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:09,940
that I’d be with you forever.

55
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:11,820
When you got married,

56
00:03:12,180 --> 00:03:13,540
I’d follow you to your husband’s place.

57
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:16,660
You two would enjoy a happy marriage

58
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:18,780
while I’d serve both of you with joy.

59
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:21,340
In the future, I’d look after your children, too.

60
00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:24,660
Then I lost my mind

61
00:03:25,220 --> 00:03:26,020
and made mistakes.

62
00:03:26,340 --> 00:03:27,820
Thankfully, you were sober

63
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:28,900
and decisive.

64
00:03:30,340 --> 00:03:32,420
I resented you back then.

65
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:34,140
I thought however good that man was,

66
00:03:34,260 --> 00:03:35,420
he wasn’t the one I love.

67
00:03:36,740 --> 00:03:37,580
Right now,

68
00:03:38,100 --> 00:03:39,660
seeing the healthy boy

69
00:03:39,780 --> 00:03:40,780
in my arms

70
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:42,340
and tears my husband shed

71
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:45,100
out of excitement,

72
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:46,620
I feel as if

73
00:03:46,780 --> 00:03:48,620
I were reborn.

74
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:50,860
But Miss,

75
00:03:51,980 --> 00:03:54,180
when I’m...grateful for you,

76
00:03:54,980 --> 00:03:56,100
my heart aches for you,

77
00:03:58,980 --> 00:03:59,740
Miss.

78
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:06,460
I’m sure Huan and her husband

79
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:08,340
are a sweet couple.

80
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:30,340
Qiuhe.

81
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:44,820
Have a look.

82
00:04:58,060 --> 00:04:58,900
Qiuhe.

83
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:02,860
I like you

84
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:04,980
and I’m willing

85
00:05:05,140 --> 00:05:07,140
to let you stay and help me.

86
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:10,420
But

87
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:12,460
I was wrong

88
00:05:12,460 --> 00:05:13,740
about Cui Bai.

89
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:17,020
He isn’t a playboy that I thought at first.

90
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:20,140
Lately, he’s made a name of himself.

91
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:22,380
His Majesty and scholars

92
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:23,580
are fond of his paintings.

93
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:27,180
Prime Minister Yan tried to set him up

94
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:29,740
with the eldest daughter

95
00:05:29,740 --> 00:05:30,780
of another famous artist

96
00:05:32,580 --> 00:05:35,300
but he turned him down.

97
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:38,340
He said

98
00:05:38,340 --> 00:05:40,260
he’s already in love with someone else.

99
00:05:40,980 --> 00:05:42,420
He always values freedom.

100
00:05:43,180 --> 00:05:45,260
If he can’t marry the woman he loves

101
00:05:45,660 --> 00:05:46,900
and travel around the world with her,

102
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:48,940
he’d rather be alone

103
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:50,220
and live a carefree life.

104
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:56,460
Qiuhe.

105
00:05:58,540 --> 00:05:59,260
What about you?

106
00:06:00,340 --> 00:06:01,860
Do you love him?

107
00:06:12,660 --> 00:06:13,420
I...

108
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:15,740
I hate to leave Your Highness,

109
00:06:16,860 --> 00:06:18,180
but he had men

110
00:06:18,260 --> 00:06:19,980
take care of my father and grandfather.

111
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:23,620
I...I appreciate that.

112
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:27,980
A group of senior servants

113
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:30,940
are able to leave the palace

114
00:06:30,940 --> 00:06:32,460
in six months.

115
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,340
I’ll tell Officer Ren

116
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:37,980
that your father is an injured veteran.

117
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:39,260
He’s all alone

118
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:40,900
and needs constant care.

119
00:06:41,900 --> 00:06:43,860
You can leave with those servants.

120
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:46,540
But Mr. Zhang

121
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:48,460
also helped me a great deal.

122
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:50,020
I haven’t got to pay him back.

123
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:52,740
Your grandfather didn’t fit to work in the army.

124
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:55,580
Any decent official

125
00:06:55,620 --> 00:06:56,780
would do the same thing.

126
00:06:57,420 --> 00:06:59,140
Maoze simply followed the rules.

127
00:06:59,660 --> 00:07:00,700
Don’t take it to heart.

128
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:12,900
Last time, I heard you had a poor appetite

129
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:14,020
and lost a lot of weight,

130
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:15,500
so I prepared

131
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:17,300
these desserts for you.

132
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:36,060
It’s sour, sweet and it smells good.

133
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:37,740
The crust is crispy.

134
00:07:39,100 --> 00:07:40,460
The stuffing

135
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:42,340
is made of sweet plum jam

136
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:43,180
and fresh pistils

137
00:07:43,540 --> 00:07:44,900
from this year’s plum blossoms.

138
00:07:45,220 --> 00:07:46,860
Its taste is unique.

139
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:49,100
That’s so thoughtful of you.

140
00:07:50,740 --> 00:07:52,500
Lately, my husband is in a bad mood

141
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:53,420
and has no appetite to eat,

142
00:07:53,620 --> 00:07:54,940
so I tried

143
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:56,740
to cheer him up with new foods.

144
00:07:57,060 --> 00:07:58,860
They worked and he could eat more.

145
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:00,700
Then it came to me

146
00:08:00,940 --> 00:08:02,340
that you’ve been sick for a while.

147
00:08:02,660 --> 00:08:04,860
Perhaps you also want to have

148
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:06,380
some sweet and sour desserts.

149
00:08:07,100 --> 00:08:07,860
Well,

150
00:08:08,060 --> 00:08:09,460
only the ones for you

151
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:11,900
were molded into various flowers.

152
00:08:12,460 --> 00:08:14,020
Only you

153
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,980
are as gorgeous as them.

154
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:22,580
What’s bothering Deputy Censor Wang?

155
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:27,580
It’s Ouyang Xiu again.

156
00:08:28,620 --> 00:08:30,860
He used to mock my husband

157
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:32,700
with his personal affairs,

158
00:08:33,180 --> 00:08:35,340
and now, he’s started to attack him directly,

159
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:38,260
calling him...calling him useless.

160
00:08:39,660 --> 00:08:40,700
That’s pure jealousy.

161
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:44,940
Your husband made principal graduate at 19.

162
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:46,260
He’s honest and humble.

163
00:08:46,380 --> 00:08:47,340
His Majesty is fond of him.

164
00:08:48,060 --> 00:08:49,420
Ouyang Xiu is no match for him!

165
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:51,580
He failed the exam twice

166
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:54,020
and only passed it when Yan Shu was in charge.

167
00:08:55,380 --> 00:08:56,580
They’re on the same side.

168
00:08:56,820 --> 00:08:58,700
Maybe there’s self-dealing between them.

169
00:09:02,180 --> 00:09:04,500
By the way, Lantiao,

170
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:07,980
go get prepared.

171
00:09:08,220 --> 00:09:10,020
Sing Dreaming of the South for Mrs. Xue.

172
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:13,100
Yes.

173
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:20,420
Half a month ago,

174
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:23,100
Investigating Censor Liang Jian
retired due to illness.

175
00:09:23,780 --> 00:09:25,860
Then I took over his case

176
00:09:26,260 --> 00:09:28,020
about Governor of Qing County

177
00:09:28,460 --> 00:09:30,140
Teng Zongliang’s embezzlement

178
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:31,420
and continued the investigation.

179
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:34,060
Deputy Censor Wang rose from a scholar.

180
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:35,340
How come your choice of word

181
00:09:35,340 --> 00:09:37,020
is so casual?

182
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:38,940
Liang Jian accused Teng Zongliang

183
00:09:39,020 --> 00:09:41,300
of misusing public funds.

184
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,580
Whether it’s true or not

185
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:43,780
remains undecided.

186
00:09:43,860 --> 00:09:45,700
How come you called it embezzlement?

187
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:47,980
Your Majesty,

188
00:09:48,540 --> 00:09:49,580
as humble as I am,

189
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:51,300
I passed the three exams

190
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:52,900
and topped the list.

191
00:09:53,220 --> 00:09:54,620
I may not be well-versed in writing,

192
00:09:54,980 --> 00:09:55,980
but I can choose the word properly.

193
00:09:56,740 --> 00:09:58,420
Censor Liang called it misuse

194
00:09:58,780 --> 00:09:59,860
while I redefined it as embezzlement

195
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:01,580
due to the progress

196
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:02,860
in my investigation.

197
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:05,740
What did you find, Gongchen?

198
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:08,100
I received Yan Du’s letter yesterday.

199
00:10:08,260 --> 00:10:09,180
It said

200
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:10,780
he had checked Teng Zongliang’s account books

201
00:10:11,060 --> 00:10:12,580
when Teng governed Qing County.

202
00:10:12,940 --> 00:10:14,180
When he followed the leads in the books

203
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:16,300
to investigate officials given public funds,

204
00:10:16,780 --> 00:10:18,260
Teng Zongliang took the chance

205
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:19,300
of not being in custody

206
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:20,500
and burned all the account books

207
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,940
dating back to his time in Wei County.

208
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,460
The only reason he wasn’t in custody

209
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:29,460
during the investigation

210
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:32,620
was that Minister Fan and Scholar Ouyang

211
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:33,700
vouched for him.

212
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:36,260
Without those account books,

213
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,180
the investigation can’t continue.

214
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:40,140
If he didn’t destroy the evidence

215
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:41,380
because he’s guilty of embezzlement,

216
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:43,500
why else did he do that?

217
00:11:07,260 --> 00:11:11,140
♪ Willows in the south ♪

218
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:13,980
♪ Leaves are too small to form shade ♪

219
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:21,540
♪ Too tender to be picked ♪

220
00:11:22,540 --> 00:11:29,180
♪ Branches are too soft even for birds ♪

221
00:11:29,180 --> 00:11:36,340
♪ Wait till late spring ♪

222
00:11:39,180 --> 00:11:40,340
What do you think?

223
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:44,820
Your taste is always impeccable.

224
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:48,900
It’s a verse

225
00:11:49,260 --> 00:11:51,100
written by the leading scholar Ouyang Xiu.

226
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:55,220
Ouyang Xiu?

227
00:11:56,940 --> 00:12:00,180
I gave it to Lantiao to sing.

228
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:03,420
Lantiao, stop.

229
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:06,940
Tell Mrs. Xue

230
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:09,140
what those scholars

231
00:12:09,980 --> 00:12:11,700
and officials

232
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:12,660
said in the theater.

233
00:12:15,340 --> 00:12:17,500
I heard that they’d ask

234
00:12:17,740 --> 00:12:19,300
young girls

235
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:21,420
to sing this.

236
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:23,900
They don’t care about the girls’ skills

237
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:25,340
as long as

238
00:12:25,340 --> 00:12:26,780
they’re young and tender enough.

239
00:12:27,420 --> 00:12:28,700
That’s what those men are craving for.

240
00:12:32,580 --> 00:12:35,020
A seemingly decent official before His Majesty

241
00:12:35,900 --> 00:12:37,260
secretly fancies such vulgar

242
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:38,740
and nasty rubbish.

243
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:41,660
What an animal!

244
00:12:43,020 --> 00:12:46,260
Your Majesty, permission to speak.

245
00:12:46,900 --> 00:12:47,780
Granted.

246
00:12:49,580 --> 00:12:51,580
I can vouch for Teng Zongliang

247
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:53,020
with my life

248
00:12:53,540 --> 00:12:55,020
that he didn’t pocket public funds.

249
00:12:55,900 --> 00:12:56,860
If it’s found

250
00:12:56,860 --> 00:12:58,660
that a copper of public money

251
00:12:58,740 --> 00:13:00,580
went to his private savings,

252
00:13:02,980 --> 00:13:05,660
I’ll...take the responsibility with him.

253
00:13:10,140 --> 00:13:12,180
I’ll keep you alive for now.

254
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:14,860
Explain to me

255
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:17,740
why are you so certain

256
00:13:18,140 --> 00:13:20,540
that he didn’t steal from public funds?

257
00:13:22,540 --> 00:13:24,460
Thank you, Your Majesty.

258
00:13:29,580 --> 00:13:32,060
First, according to Censor Liang,

259
00:13:32,340 --> 00:13:34,460
Teng Zongliang used 160,000 taels of silver.

260
00:13:34,820 --> 00:13:35,980
As far as I know,

261
00:13:36,220 --> 00:13:37,580
a local administration’s total funds

262
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:39,420
are nowhere near that number.

263
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:40,780
I’m sure

264
00:13:41,140 --> 00:13:43,100
Ministries of Revenue and War

265
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:44,500
are well aware of that.

266
00:13:50,300 --> 00:13:51,140
Your Majesty,

267
00:13:51,180 --> 00:13:53,420
= Wang Yaochen, courtesy name Boyong =

268
00:13:53,420 --> 00:13:55,460
Minister Fan is right.

269
00:13:56,220 --> 00:13:57,020
I assume

270
00:13:57,460 --> 00:13:59,580
Censor Liang

271
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:02,140
mistook the 150,000 taels of military expense

272
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:04,260
as the public fund.

273
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:07,500
He might’ve

274
00:14:08,220 --> 00:14:09,620
made a mistake there.

275
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:12,060
The Investigating Censor

276
00:14:12,740 --> 00:14:15,260
couldn’t tell military expenses from public funds

277
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:16,900
before making accusations.

278
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:19,780
How did the Censorate select their officials?

279
00:14:20,700 --> 00:14:21,980
Half a month ago,

280
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:23,460
Censor Liang retired out of illness

281
00:14:23,980 --> 00:14:24,900
and he passed away three days ago.

282
00:14:25,620 --> 00:14:27,420
Are you going after the deceased, Ouyang Xiu?

283
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:30,180
Assigning the case to the old and muddleheaded

284
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:32,260
shows that the Censorate has no...

285
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:38,740
Continue.

286
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:41,380
Second,

287
00:14:42,420 --> 00:14:44,180
the amount Teng Zongliang used

288
00:14:44,580 --> 00:14:45,900
is over 3,000.

289
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,740
Whether it’s misuse or not,

290
00:14:49,220 --> 00:14:51,660
Your Majesty can make your own judgment.

291
00:14:55,420 --> 00:14:58,020
Ge Huaimin was defeated and retreated to the west.

292
00:14:58,700 --> 00:15:00,900
Local officials were overwhelmed.

293
00:15:01,140 --> 00:15:02,940
There was no force in Jingzhou

294
00:15:03,300 --> 00:15:04,140
while Xixia troops

295
00:15:04,140 --> 00:15:05,860
were 120 miles away from Wei County.

296
00:15:06,500 --> 00:15:08,100
Teng Zongliang remained composed.

297
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:10,420
He recruited

298
00:15:10,820 --> 00:15:12,260
thousands of strong men in the neighborhood

299
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:13,860
and paid them

300
00:15:13,940 --> 00:15:15,100
to guard the city.

301
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:19,300
At that time, it was freezing outside.

302
00:15:19,740 --> 00:15:20,860
The morale was low.

303
00:15:21,740 --> 00:15:23,220
So Teng Zongliang

304
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:26,300
bought cows and sheep from farmers

305
00:15:26,780 --> 00:15:28,100
to cheer the troops up with a big meal and liquor.

306
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:31,420
Seeing that we were greatly encouraged

307
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:32,900
and our morale was rising,

308
00:15:33,580 --> 00:15:35,820
and considering their losses in previous battles,

309
00:15:36,380 --> 00:15:37,420
Xixia troops retreated.

310
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:39,300
About that,

311
00:15:40,140 --> 00:15:42,220
I think Teng Zongliang’s only mistake

312
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:44,460
was to buy cows and sheep

313
00:15:44,620 --> 00:15:45,700
with public funds

314
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:47,740
but it was for the sake of the state.

315
00:15:48,420 --> 00:15:50,420
Under that circumstance,

316
00:15:50,780 --> 00:15:51,780
it’s forgivable.

317
00:15:52,820 --> 00:15:54,020
Liang Jian reported that Zongliang

318
00:15:54,020 --> 00:15:55,420
entertained himself in Binzhou for days.

319
00:15:55,740 --> 00:15:56,780
Singers and dancers

320
00:15:56,900 --> 00:15:59,020
were rewarded with dozens of silver pieces...

321
00:16:07,820 --> 00:16:08,620
Hence,

322
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:12,580
Teng Zongliang took over 3,000 taels
from public funds

323
00:16:12,940 --> 00:16:15,140
to go through emergencies,

324
00:16:15,660 --> 00:16:16,820
reward his troops,

325
00:16:17,140 --> 00:16:18,300
stabilize the Qiang people

326
00:16:18,300 --> 00:16:19,700
and comfort the bereaved.

327
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:20,780
He didn’t pocket the money.

328
00:16:21,860 --> 00:16:23,980
There are violations of the rules,

329
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:26,940
such as doing business with public money

330
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:28,660
whose profits were given to the troops,

331
00:16:29,220 --> 00:16:31,940
and hiring harlots for entertainment on holidays.

332
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:35,380
But the northwest is poor and cold.

333
00:16:35,900 --> 00:16:37,100
When enemies came,

334
00:16:37,380 --> 00:16:38,900
they had to fight with their lives.

335
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:42,660
They could die at any minute.

336
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:45,380
I didn’t regard myself

337
00:16:46,180 --> 00:16:47,980
as a pleasure-seeking person,

338
00:16:48,660 --> 00:16:50,500
but I was tortured by the storm in the west,

339
00:16:50,900 --> 00:16:52,740
I couldn’t help feeling depressed and lonely

340
00:16:53,260 --> 00:16:55,460
which made me realize

341
00:16:55,940 --> 00:16:57,020
that others might feel the same.

342
00:16:57,740 --> 00:17:00,980
So I also hired harlots to entertain ourselves

343
00:17:01,580 --> 00:17:02,820
to reduce the loneliness

344
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:05,660
and provided financial aid to soldiers’ parents

345
00:17:05,740 --> 00:17:08,460
who were poor and alone with public funds.

346
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:10,980
Teng Zongliang only did

347
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:13,060
what Han Qi and I had done

348
00:17:13,060 --> 00:17:14,020
when we were in charge.

349
00:17:14,580 --> 00:17:15,940
If we’re found not guilty

350
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:18,340
but Teng Zongliang is,

351
00:17:18,820 --> 00:17:20,180
won’t that be unfair?

352
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:22,660
He managed

353
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:25,220
to stabilize the troops in the crisis.

354
00:17:25,620 --> 00:17:27,940
If he’s punished for using too many public funds,

355
00:17:29,100 --> 00:17:30,740
won’t that discourage

356
00:17:30,820 --> 00:17:31,940
the entire army at the border?

357
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:40,660
Your Majesty.

358
00:17:42,660 --> 00:17:44,820
General Di Qing is waiting outside.

359
00:17:55,420 --> 00:17:56,700
Mr. Fan,

360
00:17:57,500 --> 00:17:59,820
did you bring Di Qing into the palace?

361
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:01,940
Yes.

362
00:18:04,740 --> 00:18:06,300
Yan Du’s means of investigation

363
00:18:06,660 --> 00:18:07,820
may be flawed.

364
00:18:09,100 --> 00:18:11,140
You and Ouyang Xiu have made it clear.

365
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:14,100
Who allowed General Di

366
00:18:14,740 --> 00:18:15,780
to come to the Capital to appeal?

367
00:18:17,060 --> 00:18:18,180
You voiced

368
00:18:18,180 --> 00:18:19,860
that we shouldn’t be too strict with the troops

369
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:21,140
who safeguard our nation.

370
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:23,140
Does that mean

371
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:24,540
their military merits enable them

372
00:18:24,540 --> 00:18:25,740
to ride roughshod over state laws?

373
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:32,660
Di Qing’s action

374
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:34,460
is against the law

375
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:35,460
and he should be punished.

376
00:18:36,060 --> 00:18:37,020
He already stated

377
00:18:37,020 --> 00:18:38,500
that he’d take full responsibility.

378
00:18:39,420 --> 00:18:40,580
But he didn’t come

379
00:18:41,060 --> 00:18:42,500
for personal affairs.

380
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:43,940
I think

381
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:46,420
before sentencing him,

382
00:18:46,820 --> 00:18:48,740
let him tell Your Majesty

383
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:50,460
about the construction of Shuiluo City.

384
00:18:51,140 --> 00:18:53,700
It concerns the security of the border

385
00:18:54,860 --> 00:18:56,340
and it’s imperative.

386
00:18:58,100 --> 00:18:59,140
Shuiluo City?

387
00:19:01,060 --> 00:19:01,700
Pass it to me.

388
00:19:02,940 --> 00:19:03,740
Give it to me.

389
00:19:04,540 --> 00:19:05,700
Be careful! Slowly!

390
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:07,180
Princess,

391
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:08,980
would you like to play hide-and-seek?

392
00:19:08,980 --> 00:19:09,620
Sure.

393
00:19:09,820 --> 00:19:10,420
I’ll seek.

394
00:19:10,420 --> 00:19:11,980
- You two go hide. I’ll seek. - Yes.

395
00:19:13,300 --> 00:19:19,700
= The Fourth Princess Yaoyao =
One, two, three, four, five.

396
00:19:20,540 --> 00:19:21,660
Let’s see.

397
00:19:21,980 --> 00:19:22,980
Careful, or you’ll fall.

398
00:19:23,220 --> 00:19:23,940
Hurry up.

399
00:19:23,940 --> 00:19:25,020
Or she’ll catch up with us.

400
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:27,180
How about we hide over there?

401
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:28,460
Let’s go, princess.

402
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:29,300
Here it is.

403
00:19:29,460 --> 00:19:31,500
Be careful. Careful.

404
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:33,020
= Bitao =
Hurry. Let’s go.

405
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:42,780
Princess, let’s go over there.

406
00:19:44,220 --> 00:19:45,220
Let’s go...

407
00:19:45,460 --> 00:19:46,180
Not here.

408
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:47,540
We’ll be found immediately.

409
00:19:47,740 --> 00:19:48,580
Let’s get out.

410
00:19:48,740 --> 00:19:49,460
Come.

411
00:19:49,820 --> 00:19:51,180
Yes. Go over there.

412
00:19:51,260 --> 00:19:52,260
Look, over there.

413
00:19:52,260 --> 00:19:53,300
No one will find us.

414
00:19:54,780 --> 00:19:56,180
We’re safe here.

415
00:19:56,180 --> 00:19:57,660
Yes. She won’t find us.

416
00:20:02,660 --> 00:20:05,420
Princess, don’t make a sound.

417
00:20:05,740 --> 00:20:06,700
Be quiet.

418
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:07,780
Watch your hands. Good.

419
00:20:27,580 --> 00:20:28,740
I understand

420
00:20:29,260 --> 00:20:31,340
the consequence of my unauthorized visit

421
00:20:32,740 --> 00:20:33,900
but as Liu Hu said,

422
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:36,900
he should be punished for disobeying the order

423
00:20:37,300 --> 00:20:38,660
but Shuiluo City is innocent.

424
00:20:39,980 --> 00:20:41,260
Liu Hu and I didn’t get along well.

425
00:20:42,060 --> 00:20:42,940
I arrested him

426
00:20:43,260 --> 00:20:44,260
for his disobedience

427
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:46,340
but I admire his loyalty and bravery.

428
00:20:47,700 --> 00:20:49,020
Although he’s under arrest,

429
00:20:49,780 --> 00:20:50,860
I feel obligated to report

430
00:20:50,860 --> 00:20:52,100
the situation about Shuiluo City

431
00:20:53,580 --> 00:20:54,820
to Your Majesty for thorough review.

432
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:56,940
Liu Hu and I are willing to die

433
00:20:57,260 --> 00:21:00,540
as long as Shuiluo City can be built.

434
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:11,300
Alright. You may rise.

435
00:21:17,060 --> 00:21:20,020
I understand your petition

436
00:21:20,460 --> 00:21:21,620
and I’m convinced.

437
00:21:25,060 --> 00:21:26,020
If you don’t stand up,

438
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:27,460
who can I send

439
00:21:27,660 --> 00:21:29,220
to release Liu Hu

440
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:30,340
to let him redeem himself?

441
00:21:35,740 --> 00:21:38,620
A few days ago, Princess Fukang asked me

442
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:41,100
if the years were all good

443
00:21:41,260 --> 00:21:42,820
during the reign of Emperor Yao.

444
00:21:43,700 --> 00:21:45,860
I suddenly realized

445
00:21:46,780 --> 00:21:47,620
that during that period,

446
00:21:48,060 --> 00:21:51,620
demons were said to wreak havoc in the world.

447
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:53,700
When disasters occurred,

448
00:21:54,460 --> 00:21:56,100
the ruler’s only choice

449
00:21:56,460 --> 00:21:57,820
was to appoint talents to handle them.

450
00:21:58,820 --> 00:21:59,620
So,

451
00:22:00,060 --> 00:22:02,340
Emperor Yao assigned the talented Hou Yi

452
00:22:02,580 --> 00:22:05,180
to shoot down suns to pacify people.

453
00:22:05,700 --> 00:22:07,980
Hou Yi’s prowess was unrivaled

454
00:22:08,860 --> 00:22:10,620
but his personality was flawed.

455
00:22:11,620 --> 00:22:13,380
Even the flawless Emperor Yao

456
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:15,020
could accept Hou Yi.

457
00:22:15,300 --> 00:22:17,340
I’m not half as good.

458
00:22:17,860 --> 00:22:19,780
How could I expect my officials

459
00:22:20,260 --> 00:22:21,500
to be flawless?

460
00:22:41,740 --> 00:22:45,100
Teng Zongliang, Liu Hu and Di Qing

461
00:22:46,180 --> 00:22:47,580
are pillars of our state.

462
00:22:48,420 --> 00:22:49,460
Their mistakes are made

463
00:22:49,740 --> 00:22:51,380
for the greater good.

464
00:22:52,340 --> 00:22:53,500
Also, different rules

465
00:22:54,140 --> 00:22:56,500
should be applied in wartime.

466
00:22:58,140 --> 00:22:59,300
After today’s deliberation,

467
00:22:59,780 --> 00:23:00,580
I believe

468
00:23:01,100 --> 00:23:03,260
the constriction of Shuiluo City should continue.

469
00:23:03,860 --> 00:23:05,820
Three ministries should check the accounts

470
00:23:06,060 --> 00:23:06,860
and allocate the funds.

471
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:11,660
Liu Hu should be punished for his offense,

472
00:23:12,540 --> 00:23:14,540
but no one knows Shuiluo City

473
00:23:14,580 --> 00:23:16,700
and minorities there

474
00:23:17,180 --> 00:23:18,180
better than him.

475
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:21,340
He’ll be down a rank

476
00:23:21,340 --> 00:23:22,300
and deducted three months’ salary

477
00:23:22,540 --> 00:23:24,260
while continuing his previous work.

478
00:23:26,180 --> 00:23:27,340
Teng Zongliang

479
00:23:27,580 --> 00:23:28,540
is a respected general at the border

480
00:23:28,940 --> 00:23:31,100
who managed to stabilize the troops in time.

481
00:23:31,580 --> 00:23:33,620
He did use public funds

482
00:23:33,620 --> 00:23:37,340
and hired harlots to entertain his men,

483
00:23:37,460 --> 00:23:38,780
but those actions are forgivable.

484
00:23:39,620 --> 00:23:40,860
He burned the account books

485
00:23:41,500 --> 00:23:43,420
partly because of the censor’s improper methods

486
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:45,140
of interrogation.

487
00:23:47,020 --> 00:23:49,180
Demote Teng Zongliang

488
00:23:49,340 --> 00:23:50,900
to Scholar of the Hall of Articles.

489
00:23:51,700 --> 00:23:55,900
Transfer him from Qing County to Fengxiang.

490
00:23:57,140 --> 00:23:59,420
Di Qing came to the Capital without permission

491
00:24:00,420 --> 00:24:02,860
but his motive is selfless.

492
00:24:03,740 --> 00:24:05,980
He’s dedicated his heart and soul

493
00:24:06,180 --> 00:24:07,460
to our state.

494
00:24:07,780 --> 00:24:10,020
For that, he should be rewarded.

495
00:24:11,140 --> 00:24:13,620
Di Qing can take a rest today

496
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:15,460
and go to Shunde Prison tomorrow

497
00:24:15,460 --> 00:24:16,420
to release Liu Hu

498
00:24:16,940 --> 00:24:19,260
and escort him back to Shuiluo City.

499
00:24:19,860 --> 00:24:22,580
He’ll be up a rank and given 300 taels of gold.

500
00:24:58,700 --> 00:24:59,460
Princess?

501
00:25:01,860 --> 00:25:02,660
Princess.

502
00:25:22,740 --> 00:25:23,500
Xiwen,

503
00:25:24,100 --> 00:25:27,220
your well-founded speech turned the tables,

504
00:25:27,580 --> 00:25:28,740
and you suggested that Di Qing be heard.

505
00:25:29,220 --> 00:25:30,620
His Majesty will no longer

506
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:31,980
suspect us of cliquism.

507
00:25:32,540 --> 00:25:33,140
Next...

508
00:25:33,140 --> 00:25:34,860
No longer suspect us of cliquism?

509
00:25:37,980 --> 00:25:38,700
Zhigui,

510
00:25:39,700 --> 00:25:42,180
you were against the construction of Shuiluo City

511
00:25:42,420 --> 00:25:43,820
simply because you knew little

512
00:25:43,820 --> 00:25:44,740
about the situation there.

513
00:25:45,060 --> 00:25:46,060
Affairs at the border...

514
00:25:46,060 --> 00:25:47,140
I’m not saying that.

515
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:50,980
I mean His Majesty’s suspicion about cliquism.

516
00:25:53,740 --> 00:25:55,980
What do you think, Xiwen?

517
00:26:00,940 --> 00:26:01,780
I guess

518
00:26:02,540 --> 00:26:04,620
I pushed His Majesty too hard this time.

519
00:26:05,340 --> 00:26:07,020
Even though he trusts my personality

520
00:26:07,020 --> 00:26:09,260
and things I said,

521
00:26:10,380 --> 00:26:12,660
he might feel uncomfortable inside

522
00:26:13,860 --> 00:26:14,700
and that

523
00:26:14,700 --> 00:26:17,180
I meant to force him to follow my advice.

524
00:26:18,180 --> 00:26:20,980
His Majesty can dislike me

525
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:23,860
but if he thinks us together

526
00:26:24,340 --> 00:26:25,820
is bad for the reform...

527
00:26:28,140 --> 00:26:29,020
I’ll hand in

528
00:26:29,180 --> 00:26:31,460
a proposal regarding the defense in Shaanxi later

529
00:26:32,340 --> 00:26:34,900
and ask to go there to inspect

530
00:26:35,060 --> 00:26:37,300
since the treaty has just been signed

531
00:26:37,540 --> 00:26:39,780
and the border is still unsafe.

532
00:26:42,460 --> 00:26:44,460
That’s...that’s too much.

533
00:27:22,540 --> 00:27:25,300
Madam Zhang was bleeding heavily

534
00:27:25,940 --> 00:27:27,740
due to excessive shock and grief.

535
00:27:28,660 --> 00:27:30,540
The bleeding has been stopped

536
00:27:31,540 --> 00:27:33,580
and medicine has been given to soothe her.

537
00:27:34,060 --> 00:27:36,820
She’s asleep for now.

538
00:27:38,460 --> 00:27:39,780
Prin...Princess...

539
00:27:40,740 --> 00:27:43,300
Princess had an asthmatic attack.

540
00:27:43,700 --> 00:27:45,460
Without timely treatment,

541
00:27:45,980 --> 00:27:46,860
she suffocated...

542
00:27:48,420 --> 00:27:51,500
It’s likely...it’s likely that it was warm inside

543
00:27:51,580 --> 00:27:52,620
and too cold outside.

544
00:27:53,140 --> 00:27:54,500
The temperature varied...

545
00:27:55,180 --> 00:27:55,780
That’s why...

546
00:27:55,780 --> 00:27:57,540
Who found Yaoyao first?

547
00:27:58,820 --> 00:28:00,020
Who was it?

548
00:28:00,180 --> 00:28:00,900
It was me.

549
00:28:02,340 --> 00:28:04,500
I was about to show Mrs. Xue out

550
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:06,340
and heard a scream.

551
00:28:07,260 --> 00:28:08,340
Then I saw Ying’er

552
00:28:08,780 --> 00:28:09,500
stumbling in

553
00:28:09,500 --> 00:28:11,020
holding the princess.

554
00:28:13,460 --> 00:28:14,100
Princess...

555
00:28:14,700 --> 00:28:15,980
Princess lay softly

556
00:28:15,980 --> 00:28:17,140
in her arms.

557
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:19,900
Mrs. Xue noticed her condition immediately.

558
00:28:21,260 --> 00:28:22,180
She asked maids

559
00:28:22,260 --> 00:28:24,060
to call the Imperial Physicians

560
00:28:24,260 --> 00:28:25,780
while trying to save her.

561
00:28:26,940 --> 00:28:28,660
We patted her chest.

562
00:28:29,260 --> 00:28:32,340
Mrs. Xue also blew air into her mouth.

563
00:28:32,580 --> 00:28:33,340
But...

564
00:28:34,740 --> 00:28:35,380
But...

565
00:28:37,940 --> 00:28:40,580
I tried everything to save princess.

566
00:28:41,100 --> 00:28:43,340
I pressed her acupoints,

567
00:28:43,340 --> 00:28:44,100
blew air into her mouth

568
00:28:44,620 --> 00:28:48,500
until...until the Imperial Physicians arrived

569
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:52,660
and declared her death.

570
00:29:02,100 --> 00:29:02,980
Where’s that maid?

571
00:29:05,140 --> 00:29:06,700
How long has she been in the palace?

572
00:29:09,820 --> 00:29:11,100
The two maids

573
00:29:13,580 --> 00:29:16,940
are...both around ten years old.

574
00:29:18,140 --> 00:29:19,620
They came into the palace at five.

575
00:29:20,740 --> 00:29:23,860
After the Third Princess was born,

576
00:29:24,980 --> 00:29:26,580
they were selected

577
00:29:26,580 --> 00:29:27,620
to serve her.

578
00:29:32,420 --> 00:29:33,500
I remember.

579
00:29:35,900 --> 00:29:36,820
Back then,

580
00:29:39,260 --> 00:29:40,660
I picked them myself

581
00:29:40,660 --> 00:29:41,820
to be Chuyue’s playmates.

582
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:46,100
I went out earlier to run an errand.

583
00:29:46,100 --> 00:29:48,660
When I came back, it was already a mess.

584
00:29:50,580 --> 00:29:52,900
Madam Zhang couldn’t handle the princess’s death.

585
00:29:53,340 --> 00:29:56,620
She fainted and was bleeding heavily.

586
00:29:57,140 --> 00:29:58,660
When she was treated,

587
00:29:58,660 --> 00:30:00,620
I went to find who was with the princess

588
00:30:00,620 --> 00:30:02,540
and realized I forgot

589
00:30:02,540 --> 00:30:05,180
to look for those two good-for-nothings.

590
00:30:06,380 --> 00:30:07,020
Enough.

591
00:30:07,020 --> 00:30:07,740
Your Majesty...

592
00:30:13,580 --> 00:30:14,860
Under that circumstance,

593
00:30:16,660 --> 00:30:18,220
saving life was more important.

594
00:30:20,780 --> 00:30:21,500
Later...

595
00:30:22,300 --> 00:30:23,540
Later, Deputy Officer Yang

596
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:26,220
conducted a search in the palace

597
00:30:26,420 --> 00:30:27,700
and found one of them.

598
00:30:28,460 --> 00:30:29,180
When she...

599
00:30:29,300 --> 00:30:30,980
saw Deputy Officer Yang and his men,

600
00:30:31,260 --> 00:30:32,380
she panicked

601
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:34,620
and drowned herself in the lake.

602
00:30:35,460 --> 00:30:36,340
The other one...

603
00:30:37,740 --> 00:30:39,940
The other one is still missing.

604
00:30:45,180 --> 00:30:47,100
I’m so sorry, Your Majesty.

605
00:30:56,780 --> 00:30:57,700
Mother,

606
00:31:00,980 --> 00:31:02,900
are you punishing me, your unfilial son?

607
00:31:04,060 --> 00:31:04,740
Are you?

608
00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:10,820
Please tell me

609
00:31:13,580 --> 00:31:14,940
how I can redeem myself.

610
00:31:17,540 --> 00:31:18,900
How, mother?

611
00:31:49,460 --> 00:31:50,220
Mother,

612
00:31:52,900 --> 00:31:57,660
tell me how I can redeem myself.

613
00:32:10,180 --> 00:32:10,820
Xinhe.

614
00:32:12,380 --> 00:32:13,380
Go inside later.

615
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:16,180
I’ve asked Imperial Physicians

616
00:32:16,180 --> 00:32:17,340
to wait at your chamber.

617
00:32:18,300 --> 00:32:19,700
Soothing herbal soup

618
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:21,620
will also be delivered there in a few hours

619
00:32:21,660 --> 00:32:22,820
after it’s done.

620
00:32:24,740 --> 00:32:25,540
I see.

621
00:32:41,060 --> 00:32:41,940
Seven days,

622
00:32:42,860 --> 00:32:43,660
everyone,

623
00:32:44,540 --> 00:32:46,500
His Majesty hasn’t come to court for seven days.

624
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:48,660
I understand the Fourth Princess passed away,

625
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:50,660
but this is against the rules.

626
00:32:50,660 --> 00:32:51,940
What about state affairs?

627
00:32:52,780 --> 00:32:54,060
His Majesty’s making

628
00:32:54,060 --> 00:32:55,100
such an exception for Madam Zhang.

629
00:32:55,940 --> 00:32:56,820
Gentlemen,

630
00:32:57,380 --> 00:32:58,220
we should...

631
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:07,060
Prime Minister Yan.

632
00:33:16,940 --> 00:33:18,540
Prime Minister Zhang, this matter...

633
00:33:19,580 --> 00:33:20,700
= Zhang Dexiang, courtesy name Xiyan =
Scholar Ouyang,

634
00:33:21,020 --> 00:33:23,060
if you’re going to remonstrate against it,

635
00:33:23,740 --> 00:33:26,260
the Cabinet can hand in your report.

636
00:33:27,060 --> 00:33:27,980
But…

637
00:33:28,180 --> 00:33:31,460
Yongshu, the deceased princess

638
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:33,420
wasn’t just Madam Zhang’s daughter.

639
00:33:37,180 --> 00:33:38,540
I...I know.

640
00:33:39,340 --> 00:33:42,700
Men take years off to mourn their parents’ deaths

641
00:33:42,700 --> 00:33:45,500
but not the other way around.

642
00:33:46,780 --> 00:33:47,580
Others aside,

643
00:33:48,260 --> 00:33:49,260
back then,

644
00:33:50,140 --> 00:33:51,500
when the Khitans deployed troops at the border,

645
00:33:51,500 --> 00:33:52,660
Yanguo was the envoy to negotiate with them.

646
00:33:52,860 --> 00:33:54,500
He received his wife’s letter on the way

647
00:33:54,500 --> 00:33:55,780
but burned it without having a look,

648
00:33:55,780 --> 00:33:56,460
right?

649
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:58,180
He was afraid that he’d be distracted

650
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,340
by his family affair.

651
00:33:59,660 --> 00:34:00,420
He didn’t know

652
00:34:00,420 --> 00:34:01,780
his daughter was severely ill until later.

653
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:02,860
When he returned...

654
00:34:14,940 --> 00:34:16,500
Anyway, gentlemen,

655
00:34:17,780 --> 00:34:19,660
please take this matter into consideration.

656
00:34:28,180 --> 00:34:31,220
= Wang Mansion =

657
00:34:40,500 --> 00:34:41,660
This way, please, Mr. Jia.

658
00:34:57,140 --> 00:34:58,300
I’m guilty.

659
00:34:58,940 --> 00:35:00,820
Please forgive me for being unable to receive you.

660
00:35:01,620 --> 00:35:02,420
I apologize.

661
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:04,700
Deputy Censor Wang,

662
00:35:05,980 --> 00:35:09,180
who said you’re guilty?

663
00:35:11,820 --> 00:35:13,660
The Censorate accused Teng Zongliang

664
00:35:13,660 --> 00:35:14,940
of misusing public funds.

665
00:35:15,620 --> 00:35:16,940
The investigator

666
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:18,540
was a censor.

667
00:35:19,580 --> 00:35:21,100
During the investigation,

668
00:35:21,420 --> 00:35:22,940
Teng Zongliang brazenly destroyed

669
00:35:22,940 --> 00:35:24,820
key evidence.

670
00:35:25,700 --> 00:35:26,940
During the court deliberation,

671
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:29,540
Fan Zhongyan and Ouyang Xiu

672
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:30,620
made convincing speeches

673
00:35:30,620 --> 00:35:32,540
that he only destroyed the evidence

674
00:35:32,540 --> 00:35:34,860
because nobody is flawless.

675
00:35:37,020 --> 00:35:38,900
I’m ashamed of myself.

676
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:41,500
I’m not a good writer or a speaker

677
00:35:41,860 --> 00:35:44,060
as those two officials.

678
00:35:44,460 --> 00:35:47,020
My vision and talents are limited.

679
00:35:47,580 --> 00:35:49,820
Since His Majesty punished the one we believed

680
00:35:49,940 --> 00:35:51,860
was guilty of embezzlement so lightly,

681
00:35:51,940 --> 00:35:54,700
our judgment must’ve been wrong.

682
00:35:55,500 --> 00:35:57,620
I failed to recognize

683
00:35:57,620 --> 00:35:59,740
Governor Teng’s patriotism.

684
00:36:01,780 --> 00:36:04,500
I’m not virtuous or capable enough

685
00:36:04,500 --> 00:36:05,620
to hold such an important post.

686
00:36:06,380 --> 00:36:08,060
His Majesty should remove me

687
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:09,780
from office.

688
00:36:10,300 --> 00:36:10,900
You...

689
00:36:19,220 --> 00:36:20,700
I remember the Empress Dowager

690
00:36:21,660 --> 00:36:23,220
once told me

691
00:36:24,420 --> 00:36:26,300
when Madam Li was alive,

692
00:36:26,900 --> 00:36:27,820
she cared about

693
00:36:28,220 --> 00:36:29,700
her little brother the most.

694
00:36:31,260 --> 00:36:33,140
They used to support each other.

695
00:36:33,700 --> 00:36:34,940
They were the closest

696
00:36:35,980 --> 00:36:37,260
and carried the bloodline of the Li family.

697
00:36:39,620 --> 00:36:41,660
After the Empress Dowager found him,

698
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:45,820
she and Your Majesty kept rewarding him.

699
00:36:47,420 --> 00:36:48,180
Right now,

700
00:36:48,980 --> 00:36:51,460
he’s one of the ministers

701
00:36:51,780 --> 00:36:52,860
and his family is prestigious.

702
00:36:58,420 --> 00:37:00,780
No. No, no.

703
00:37:02,180 --> 00:37:03,220
Not enough.

704
00:37:04,780 --> 00:37:06,300
Uncle is always humble.

705
00:37:06,900 --> 00:37:08,100
He’s given an honorable title,

706
00:37:08,100 --> 00:37:09,380
but never abused his power.

707
00:37:09,980 --> 00:37:10,780
In wartime,

708
00:37:11,220 --> 00:37:13,020
he donated money to fund the army more than once.

709
00:37:14,940 --> 00:37:15,700
Not enough.

710
00:37:16,740 --> 00:37:18,380
His rewards are far from enough.

711
00:37:20,220 --> 00:37:20,900
Servant.

712
00:37:22,940 --> 00:37:24,220
Summon Li Yonghe to the palace immediately.

713
00:37:46,420 --> 00:37:48,620
My lady, what happened to Lord?

714
00:38:34,820 --> 00:38:38,260
Your Majesty, aren’t you going to court today?

715
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:41,260
Don’t move.

716
00:38:44,820 --> 00:38:46,020
When I came yesterday,

717
00:38:46,020 --> 00:38:47,300
you took the medicine and was sleeping,

718
00:38:47,940 --> 00:38:49,140
so I rested in the side chamber.

719
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:51,540
Just now,

720
00:38:52,700 --> 00:38:54,420
Lantiao helped me freshen up.

721
00:38:54,540 --> 00:38:55,700
I came to check on you.

722
00:38:57,380 --> 00:38:59,660
I’m already awake and can’t sleep.

723
00:39:00,780 --> 00:39:03,220
Before you come next time,

724
00:39:03,620 --> 00:39:04,980
there’s plenty of time

725
00:39:05,380 --> 00:39:06,620
for me to rest.

726
00:39:12,180 --> 00:39:12,860
Fine.

727
00:39:13,740 --> 00:39:15,220
I’ll tell them to serve breakfast.

728
00:39:16,220 --> 00:39:17,780
Have some food if you can.

729
00:39:29,580 --> 00:39:30,100
This way.

730
00:39:30,100 --> 00:39:30,780
Careful.

731
00:39:35,580 --> 00:39:36,260
Hurry.

732
00:39:36,260 --> 00:39:37,100
Slowly.

733
00:39:40,220 --> 00:39:41,220
- Over there. There. - Slowly.

734
00:39:42,700 --> 00:39:44,340
Stop running. You’re cheating.

735
00:39:44,420 --> 00:39:45,380
You’re Zuixinglai.

736
00:39:45,540 --> 00:39:46,220
You’re cheating.

737
00:39:52,180 --> 00:39:57,940
Seven, six, five, four, three, two, one.

738
00:39:58,180 --> 00:39:58,900
Stop moving.

739
00:40:00,220 --> 00:40:01,060
Zuixinglai!

740
00:40:02,660 --> 00:40:03,980
Come and catch me.

741
00:40:12,100 --> 00:40:14,220
Where is Deputy Censor

742
00:40:14,500 --> 00:40:15,660
Wang Gongchen?

743
00:40:21,020 --> 00:40:23,460
Wang Gongchen is waiting for punishment at home

744
00:40:24,700 --> 00:40:25,940
while going on a fast and reflecting himself.

745
00:40:26,500 --> 00:40:28,460
He asks His Majesty to punish and demote him.

746
00:40:28,900 --> 00:40:30,940
= Xiao Song, courtesy name Ziqiao =

747
00:40:32,060 --> 00:40:32,940
I don’t remember

748
00:40:32,940 --> 00:40:34,220
he made a mistake.

749
00:40:34,580 --> 00:40:36,380
Why does he ask for punishment?

750
00:40:37,100 --> 00:40:38,820
Wang Gongchen said in his proposal

751
00:40:39,380 --> 00:40:40,620
that Teng Zongliang

752
00:40:40,860 --> 00:40:42,420
burned the account books,

753
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:45,100
which halted the investigation.

754
00:40:45,860 --> 00:40:47,140
The Censorate believed

755
00:40:47,140 --> 00:40:49,100
destroying key evidence

756
00:40:49,180 --> 00:40:50,220
was a felony

757
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:54,860
while Minister Fan and Scholar Ouyang argued

758
00:40:55,180 --> 00:40:57,100
that the Censorate’s misconduct

759
00:40:57,900 --> 00:41:00,300
and violent interrogation left him no choice.

760
00:41:01,020 --> 00:41:03,940
Eventually, he was down a rank

761
00:41:04,300 --> 00:41:05,740
and demoted to Governor of Fengxiang.

762
00:41:06,180 --> 00:41:09,180
His punishment was too light.

763
00:41:10,530 --> 00:41:11,230
Oh.

764
00:41:12,340 --> 00:41:13,860
So he’s going on a hunger strike.

765
00:41:14,500 --> 00:41:15,500
Wang Gongchen said

766
00:41:16,100 --> 00:41:18,540
since Teng Zongliang was pardoned so easily,

767
00:41:18,820 --> 00:41:20,380
Your Majesty must’ve believed

768
00:41:20,420 --> 00:41:22,620
that he was forced

769
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:24,020
to burn the account books

770
00:41:24,140 --> 00:41:26,260
by the censor

771
00:41:26,300 --> 00:41:27,500
investigating his case

772
00:41:27,980 --> 00:41:29,900
who answers

773
00:41:30,020 --> 00:41:31,780
to Deputy Censor.

774
00:41:32,140 --> 00:41:33,820
So he finds himself guilty

775
00:41:34,180 --> 00:41:36,460
and should be demoted.

776
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:49,620
Alright.

777
00:41:50,980 --> 00:41:51,900
I see.

778
00:41:53,060 --> 00:41:54,340
I’ll reconsider it.

779
00:41:57,540 --> 00:42:00,540
My lady, you have to talk to Lord.

780
00:42:02,180 --> 00:42:04,540
He’s challenging His Majesty’s decision.

781
00:42:05,580 --> 00:42:07,420
If His Majesty is offended,

782
00:42:08,340 --> 00:42:09,180
will he...

783
00:42:09,940 --> 00:42:11,700
will he kill all of us?

784
00:42:12,380 --> 00:42:13,300
Nonsense!

785
00:42:13,300 --> 00:42:14,260
Watch your mouth!

786
00:42:14,460 --> 00:42:16,300
His Majesty has never killed officials.

787
00:42:16,940 --> 00:42:17,660
My lady.

788
00:42:19,460 --> 00:42:22,300
My lady, Deputy Officer Yang is outside.

789
00:42:25,140 --> 00:42:26,620
What did I say?

790
00:42:27,020 --> 00:42:28,300
What did I say?

791
00:42:28,620 --> 00:42:30,020
His Majesty sent people here.

792
00:42:31,540 --> 00:42:32,980
There must be a decree.

793
00:42:40,820 --> 00:42:50,460
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

794
00:42:51,820 --> 00:43:00,140
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

795
00:43:02,980 --> 00:43:07,700
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

796
00:43:08,700 --> 00:43:12,860
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

797
00:43:14,300 --> 00:43:19,780
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

798
00:43:19,780 --> 00:43:24,540
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

799
00:43:28,220 --> 00:43:33,860
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

800
00:43:33,860 --> 00:43:38,780
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

801
00:43:39,260 --> 00:43:45,020
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

802
00:43:45,020 --> 00:43:50,100
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

803
00:43:50,540 --> 00:43:55,460
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

804
00:43:56,100 --> 00:44:00,940
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

805
00:44:01,620 --> 00:44:06,780
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

806
00:44:07,300 --> 00:44:12,340
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

807
00:44:12,860 --> 00:44:16,940
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

808
00:44:18,420 --> 00:44:23,060
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

809
00:44:24,060 --> 00:44:29,220
♪ The howling wind ♪

810
00:44:29,580 --> 00:44:33,660
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

811
00:44:35,140 --> 00:44:40,060
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

812
00:44:40,740 --> 00:44:45,940
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

813
00:44:46,380 --> 00:44:51,660
♪ The howling wind ♪

814
00:44:51,940 --> 00:44:56,820
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

815
00:44:57,420 --> 00:45:04,140
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
